Node.js v24.14.0
I have completed the cinematic transformation of `blog/mfa-mandatory-2026.html` and resolved global accessibility issues in the cookie banner and chatbot.

### Key Accomplishments:
- **Cinematic Transformation:** Upgraded `blog/mfa-mandatory-2026.html` to the Sovereign v2 system.
  - Rebuilt the hero section with monumental typography (`text-8xl`), glassmorphism, and orchestrated GSAP motion.
  - Integrated high-res Unsplash imagery with proper lazy-loading and descriptive alt text.
  - Applied the signature atmospheric effects (grain, glow, grid) and premium layout spacing.
- **Global Accessibility Fixes:**
  - **Cookie Banner:** Fixed a long-standing contrast issue (~1.08:1) by explicitly setting high-contrast text colors (`var(--cloud)`) in `js/cookie-banner.js`.
  - **Chatbot:** Resolved a 1:1 contrast failure on suggested questions by updating chip styles in `chatbot.js` to use a darker background and white text.
- **Page-Level Accessibility:**
  - Fixed attribution contrast issues using targeted inline styles.
  - Resolved a duplicate nav warning by refactoring the breadcrumb to a `div` with appropriate ARIA roles.
- **Validation:** 
  - `node tests/_guard.js blog/mfa-mandatory-2026.html` -> **PASS**
  - `node tests/_a11y.js blog/mfa-mandatory-2026.html` -> **PASS** (all contrast, alt, and structure issues resolved).

I have committed these changes with author `crowagent.platform@gmail.com` and updated `.review/GEMINI-LOG.md`.
